{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1691-10_007","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Ode pour le Roy","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", octobre 1691 [tome 10], p. 7-15.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},{"#1":{"value":"Il y a long-temps, Madame, que vous estes convaincuë qu’on n’a jamais vû de Souverain qui ait soutenu la grandeur &amp; la majesté du Trône avec plus de gloire que nostre Auguste Monarque. Ainsi je n’entreray dans aucun détail des actions merveilleuses qui luy ont fait meriter le nom de Grand. Elles sont connuës de tout le monde, &amp; il n’y a point de Province où ceux que favorisent les Muses n’employent leurs talens à les celebrer. La Piece que vous allez lire m’a esté envoyée d’Avignon, &amp; M","id":"/div/p[1]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p[1]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" de Guitrandy en est l’Auteur. Vous avez déja vû un autre Ouvrage de luy dans ma Lettre du mois de Juin dernier, &amp; le plaisir que sa lecture vous a donné vous doit estre une asseurance que vous ne serez pas moins contente de celuy-cy.","id":"/div/p[1]/#2"}}],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"ODE","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"POUR LE ROY.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Grand Dieu, Providence adorable,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui veilles sur cet Univers,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qui vois d’un œil favorable","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ceux qui te vangent des Pervers,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu sçais qu’aujourd’huy sur la terre","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aucun Prince ne fait la guerre","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ceux qui méprisent tes Loix,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme LOUIS, ce grand Monarque,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au front de qui chacun remarque","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le vray caractere des Rois.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Quel autre avec un plus beau zele","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Soutient les droits de tes Autels ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel autre entre tous les Mortels","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A te servir est plus fidelle ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu sçais que dés qu’il fut monté","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur le Trône de majesté","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il fait briller d’un nouveau lustre,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il médita de saints combats,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour mettre par un coup illustre","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Crime &amp; l’Heresie à bas.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De mesme qu’en sortant de l’onde","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout environné de clarté,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Soleil chasse loin du monde","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les horreurs de l’obscurité.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’œil content de le voir renaistre,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voit en un moment disparoistre","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les tristes flambeaux de la nuit,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et fuir dans quelque roche obscure","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces Oiseaux de sinistre augure,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ennemis du jour qui leur luit.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ainsi pour montrer sa puissance,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nostre Roy par tout renommé,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et craint autant qu’il est aimé,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’eut besoin que de sa presence.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ouy, la splendeur de ses regards","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sceut dissiper tous les broüillards","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’Envie &amp; de la Malice ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’on voit dans le mesme temps","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Perir l’insolence du Vice,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’orgueil des nouveaux Titans.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Les Siecles passez, je l’avouë,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Peuvent nommer de grands Guerriers ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais pour meriter qu’on les loüe","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont-ils joint l’Olive aux Lauriers ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On a dans le cours des années","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vû mille vertus couronnées","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Succomber sous leur propre faix ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais en a-t-on vû jamais une","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui sceust maîtriser la Fortune,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dans la Guerre &amp; dans la Paix ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’éclat d’une si belle gloire","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui couvre un parfait Conquerant,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’estoit que pour Loüis le Grand,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui fait plus que l’on ne peut croire.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est par luy qu’on voit surmontez","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces cruels Monstres indomptez","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui regnoient dans toute la France.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Vol, la Fraude, le Duel,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Rebellion, l’Ignorance,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En ont receu le coup mortel.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Combien d’ambitieuses Testes","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont depuis plié sous sa main !","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Combien de terribles tempestes","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont mugy contre nous en vain !","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son bras qui rompt tous les obstacles,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Produit chaque jour des miracles","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour bien affermir cet Etat,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est, grace à ce Prince habile","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aussi bien reglé qu’une Ville,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aussi grand que son Potentat.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Luy seul parmy tant d’autres Princes","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A sceu d’un bras victorieux","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dompter ce Monstre furieux","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui ravageoit tant de Provinces","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Heresie au crin de Serpens,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Autour de sa teste siflans,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Expire sous le coup de foudre,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que ce bras secondé du Ciel,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A lancé pour la mettre en poudre.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et luy faire vomir son fiel.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Non content de cette Victoire","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui met l’Heresie au tombeau,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans nostre France que la gloire","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Couvre de son jour le plus beau,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nostre Roy, ce foudre de guerre,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La menace dans l’Angleterre,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux yeux de ses fiers Leopards.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tremble pour toy, Peuple rebelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nos Soldats brûlent d’un beau zele,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et nos Chefs sont autant de Mars.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Nos Troupes bien plus animées","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’esprit de leur Souverain,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que du son guerrier de l’airain,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A vaincre sont accoutumées.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fier Anglois, ouvre donc les yeux.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et tâche d’appaiser les Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont la colere te menace.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rien ne sçauroit t’en garantir,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et cette force qui terrasse","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne cede qu’au seul repentir.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Jacques, dont le Peuple farouche","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Suit les Loix d’un Usurpateur,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si ton sort malheureux me touche,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’admire encore ton bonheur.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu n’as desormais rien à craindre,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ton mal n’est plus tant à plaindre","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ayant nostre Alcide pour toy.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non, non, le Ciel t’est favorable,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"LOUIS t’aime, il t’est secourable,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et c’est assez pour estre Roy.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais toy, divine Providence,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Souveraine des Nations,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par qui les grandes actions","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne sont jamais sans récompense","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Daigne nous conserver LOUIS,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui dans ses Exploits inoüies","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’a point d’autre but que ta gloire,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’il combat, c’est pour ta grandeur,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et s’il remporte la Victoire,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’abord il t’en nomme l’Auteur.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}}]}}}